author: The Peninsula
title: Qatar- Shaded market and parking
text: (MENAFN - The Peninsula) The Ministry of Municipality and Urban Planning has set up shades in the vegetables market at the central market to protect the produce displayed for sale, from direct sun and dust and vehicles in the parking areas. The ministry said open areas in the market will be developed and provided with shades, electricity and other services.
